#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-31-migrate-poetry-to-rye-netlify.rst:8
msgid "PoetryからRyeへの移行と、Netlifyビルドの完全対応"
msgstr "Migrating from Poetry to Rye and fully supporting Netlify builds"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-31-migrate-poetry-to-rye-netlify.rst:10
msgid ""
"Poetryで管理していたPythonプロジェクトを、最近注目されているRyeに移行し、 "
"さらにNetlifyでのデプロイまでを通して構成を整えた。この記事では、その手順と要点を記録しておく。"
msgstr ""
"I migrated the Python project that was managed with Poetry to Rye, which has"
" been attracting a lot of attention recently, and also completed the "
"configuration by deploying it with Netlify. In this article, I will record "
"the steps and key points."

